999. Fresh context each iteration - save learnings to memories for next time
1000. Don't assume 'not implemented' - search first
1001. Backpressure is law - tests/typecheck/lint/audit must pass
1002. When behavior is runnable or user-facing, exercise the real app with the strongest available harness (Playwright, tmux, real CLI/API) and try at least one adversarial path before reporting done
1003. Confidence protocol: score decisions 0-100. >80 proceed autonomously; 50-80 proceed + document in .ralph/agent/decisions.md; <50 choose safe default + document
1004. Commit atomically - one logical change per commit, capture the why

